Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: shell-mommy
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Affirmations in your terminal!
 Provides encouraging messages when running shell commands or cargo commands.
 .
 Features:
  - Both 'mommy' for shell commands and 'cargo-mommy' as a Cargo subcommand
  - Customizable roles, pronouns, emotes, and responses
  - Multiple mood systems (chill, ominous, thirsty)
  - Quiet mode for CI/CD pipelines
  - Role transformation support
  - Recursion protection
